get.description:
Return the full deprecation registry for this deployment.

Response shape::

    {
        "count": 2,
        "deprecations": [
            {
                "endpoint": "/api/v1/customers",
                "deprecated_at": "2026-04-01T00:00:00+00:00",
                "sunset_at":     "2028-04-01T00:00:00+00:00",
                "replacement_endpoint": "/api/v2/customers"
            },
            ...
        ]
    }
